name: PVFRE
description: Periferal visual field impairment right eye
details:
{yes}\\{no}
We are considering whether it is possible to work directly with the image, even though it is a PDF.
If the information will be available, the residual degrees for visual field will be provided (like 12º or 10º), example: eyes had a constricted visual field < 10. 
The format of numerical information provision is not yed defined: it could be either INT (12) or STR (12º).
This concerns all visual fields impairment variables.
